                                <p>
                                    Open the program configuration.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- /margin -->

                        <div class="margin">
                            <div>
                                <p class="justify">
                                    <strong>Step 2</strong>: In the window Basic settings please select the setting Troubleshoot on the left side.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <amp-img src="/images/Avast_Internet_Security_02_EN.jpg" width="650" height="603" layout="responsive" class="shadow"></amp-img>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- /margin -->

                        <div class="margin">
                            <div>
                                <p class="justify">
                                    <strong>Step 3</strong>: In the Troubleshooting menu please go to the section Web and select the field Ignored addresses.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <amp-img src="/images/Avast_Internet_Security_03_EN.jpg" width="650" height="603" layout="responsive" class="shadow"></amp-img>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- /margin -->

                        <div class="margin">
                            <div>
                                <p class="justify">
                                    <strong>Step 4</strong>: Please fill in the IP address of your camera. If you have more then one IP cameras please type in each IP address separated by a comma (,). Now please confirm the settings by clicking OK.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <amp-img src="/images/Avast_Internet_Security_04_EN.jpg" width="650" height="603" layout="responsive" class="shadow"></amp-img>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- /margin -->

                        <div class="margin">
                            <div>
                                <p class="justify">
                                    <strong>Step 5</strong>: Finally, please reload the web interface of your IP camera. This can be done by either clicking the refresh button next to the address bar of your web browser or you can close your web browser and re-type the IP address of your camera in the browsers address bar.
                                </p>
